Identification_Area.title: n4wl01xqq_raw.fits: Raw NICMOS data from HST Program 7885.

Modification_Detail.description:
This is the initial PDS4 version of this data product.
This FITS file was retrieved from MAST on 2024-06-20. It was originally produced by MAST on or around 2009-03-01, using version OPUS 2008_5c of their HST processing software.
Migration to the PDS4 standard was carried out by the PDS Ring-Moon Systems Node using their HST migration pipeline version 1.0 (2024-07-17) and XML labeling software version 1.0 (2023-06-26).

Observation_Area.comment: This is a copy of HST file "n4wl01xqq_raw.fits" as obtained from the Mikulski Archive for Space Telescopes (MAST) on 2024-06-20. The file was produced by MAST on or around 2009-03-01, using version OPUS 2008_5c of their HST processing pipeline.

Primary_Result_Summary.description: n4wl01xqq_raw.fits: Raw NICMOS data from HST Program 7885.

Internal_Reference.comment: n4wl01xqj_jif.fits: NICMOS 2-D jitter histogram image for the associated "_jit" file (n4wl01xqj_jit.fits, urn:nasa:pds:hst_7885:miscellaneous_nicmos_jit:n4wl01xqj::1:0) from HST Program 7885.
n4wl01xqj_jit.fits: NICMOS pointing jitter table for this NICMOS/NIC1 observation from HST Program 7885.
n4wl01xqq_cal.fits: Calibrated version of the associated "_raw" NICMOS/NIC1 data file (n4wl01xqq_raw.fits, urn:nasa:pds:hst_7885:data_nicmos_raw:n4wl01xqq::1:0) from HST Program 7885.
n4wl01xqq_ima.fits: Intermediate NICMOS MULTIACCUM data file for HST Program 7885.
n4wl01xqq_spt.fits: Support, planning, and telemetry data for this NICMOS/NIC1 observation from HST Program 7885.
n4wl01xqq_trl.fits: Trailer file with processing log for this NICMOS/NIC1 observation from HST Program 7885.
